  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-27721153-72d5-4b5d-9fe6-ef4af70a6c19\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e0d5ddf-8c6d-44a7-b9ea-8668fc6186d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c576f628-8541-41c0-81bc-5133687172e0\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>스타트업 회사 단상자</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ef01b212-9b84-4d37-be25-f36334deec4b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2f4d9648-d2c1-409f-961d-84d8db2bbe66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dad1669-54e0-4489-a707-a73d18b6ca04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러분이 스타트업 회사의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0c180c31-a199-455f-ae28-fa21d4a92950\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2232f7b2-f0b0-4478-98eb-3a24995b9847\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자를 준비하는 중이라면?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-60ba98bc-6a1d-4790-8ca5-f3667caa134b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f210982c-ceaf-4b7d-a46f-8c7cd2c91e21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음의 세 가지만 고려하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-464501a5-37bf-4a1f-9ccb-5e43ab64892a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 중요한 것은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-333885d7-b54e-40d9-8bf0-794f33499911\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0a5fd862-a6d4-46ec-9ac9-7fe4bb133fac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebb549b4-91ae-4818-ad50-4314795a07c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01a483ae-a0b4-4a3c-90f7-cff4609b1c34\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">단상자는 제품의 성격에 맞는 디자인이 중요합니다. 물론 전문 패키지 디자인 회사 또는 소속 디자이너가 작업을 하겠지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니도 30여 년이 넘는 디자인 경험을 바탕으로 가장 합리적인 비용과 높은 퀄리티로 디자인을 제공해 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca333db0-bfd8-453e-a957-917222917384\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c8dbc64-225b-47c7-9b5a-e76487d8fe48\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8465f0d5-af9c-4371-95e7-2abf7c1a712f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f31d156e-a6dd-44cc-97ad-086de317fcbb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품에 맞는 가로, 세로, 높이 즉, 장폭고를 정해야 합니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-946a35cd-bc0f-4e03-b904-fc721e35bbe7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>그 사이즈에 맞는 칼선을 요청하세요. 무료로 칼선을 제공해 드립니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f585e82a-297f-4387-a8c2-a1ea4f57a7f7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69905a89-419b-40d1-aea8-34f79b9b6d38\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8cc7646d-cc0a-448c-9579-360e83c52cb6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a334d59-cf8e-4559-9352-44d05a0c0fc8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인 회사로부터 칼선을 받으시면 그 안에 디자인을 입혀 작업하게 됩니다. 이 디자인에서 들어가야 하는 것은 여러 가지이지만 몇 가지만 추려보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc7fafb2-014f-472d-bafe-7541652d0d04\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-94524a3c-7a93-4231-b106-16536f2178ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10d993db-9e1e-4a4c-9376-1cab5ec4e1d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-af011f50-ae15-455b-a586-c1c275d62163\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일단 브랜드/로고입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37495382-c4b1-4745-a376-786260318bc5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:676px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c99a98a2-5857-4f84-a9cd-31fb54723128\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:676px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fa138816-e34e-4b80-a1a9-d5bde83d26c5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-890fb033-cfec-4679-8634-0d5d0374a7e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cd8cecb2-da00-4a6e-bf0f-111f144d06bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">통상 정면에는 브랜드 로고로 디자인을 합니다. 브랜드 로고는 반드시 제작해서 삽입해야 하는 필수 요소입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea5675d5-b885-48e7-b9df-a435460a0aea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8125d4d2-dd84-42dc-a93a-3b59af046136\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-67d9c43b-86bb-4d57-93c4-a3164f8b760b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c63d494d-1e1e-49d2-8543-7953212073f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">측면에는 이 제품의 사양이 삽입됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b4f8cce-d9dc-4b59-ba11-3c873e3ebc05\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:221px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-265d1e84-4562-49e6-8b21-ca2258c2d6a7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5fb3fa34-5a98-4c14-81a1-c9cb64c73b74\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d92074ac-f0a9-419a-8964-c8235a64f99c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 설명서는 반드시 오타나 5point 이상 읽을 수 있게 디자인해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20fa74d1-743d-442c-bc79-afd8841c91bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6d314df6-30ac-4f8f-a7bd-816e6a359a8c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca440099-ee83-4cca-80d0-758d7616de44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c076f112-52ec-45ec-a4f6-79f57b0ac011\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내용이 많다면 적은 포인트로 디자인할 수 있지만 제약조건이 있습니다. 반드시 제품 사양은 필수로 디자인하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-28771b74-22bb-4a41-a239-f2697ab15ca8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:882px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b0fe8489-89d4-412a-84c0-4c7596c9409d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abc6e47b-e954-406b-aa11-edae86d1020f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbba0894-0adf-46c6-b1d4-8eb99f579a8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품의 경우 다음과 같은 성분으로 디자인할 수 있습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7852215-6764-4aca-abdc-356c91bdb95a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dd273772-682a-490e-a0a5-3c06c0ed56d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6eddb6b5-e759-4187-bdeb-87d226251eaf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e7b2ee4-aa48-43cc-93c3-f1d63de406f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또 하나 중요한 것은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-575117d0-68ca-41f0-9536-799913ecca51\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9451a5e-21b4-49e2-8ead-5af482944be4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dafb0deb-be64-4238-8b1b-b2b3f6fd4e39\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e615291-073e-4fa6-bcad-62dee34b2efc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">여러분이 스타트업이라면 생산 수량에 대해 고민해야 합니다. 오프셋인쇄 방식이라면 기본 500개에서 수만 개를 생산해서 단가를 절약하는 것이 중요합니다. 하지만 대부분의 스타트업 회사는 제품 판매의 추이를 보고 싶어 하실 겁니다. 이럴 때는 디지털 인쇄로 단가는 높더라도 수량을 줄여 제작하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71ab2ec5-bbb0-43cd-a9f2-6af34e59ab1b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c47d01f6-5d4f-4146-87c0-76e261211983\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef097a01-9fed-4633-b797-8b77ee96ba77\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39ca3e11-8b67-4295-9ee3-fb2222f8afef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 소량을 생산하면 사이즈나 종이, 수량에서 제약사항이 있습니다. 하지만 본 제품을 팔기 위해 샘플로 제작해 볼 수도 있고 100개만 이벤트성으로 제작하기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cc501a77-1be8-411e-ad9b-4fc9d30a487f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 100.0%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 2px 0px 0px 2px; border-color: #d2d2d2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #e2e2e2;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ddfaba00-5079-4cc4-a6f1-4de85b1e5493\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b111e713-837f-4a0d-865c-e81e648aa537\" style=\"\"><b>구분</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #e2e2e2;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f59138a-f26c-4f12-b914-fc8a349a38e5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1b015749-40f8-4c3b-9628-7b16e6b6a676\" style=\"\"><b>기본 수량</b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #e2e2e2;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f21f7f2-3abc-4508-9e81-81dbff0ba274\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f137c24b-428b-4948-a7c3-4af418bd9cd4\" style=\"\"><b>제약 사항</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-566ce106-6027-4014-bb17-f63cadcd1a39\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-85de17ca-04cc-447d-b4d7-1fa3b287fe84\" style=\"\">오프셋</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa48b03f-0efb-4aec-937a-5974fc9773c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8894ddb4-d5fe-45e3-8720-b3e650ab5f5b\" style=\"\">500개 이상</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34e771f3-37b1-47a6-aa40-1a31010df257\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8bd9704c-21ca-46ce-af06-2712cf1e12fe\" style=\"\">없음</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e08ae320-a540-4380-a719-c3cd179b0c1d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5457492a-9cf2-48e9-a6a4-0e93a63cb302\" style=\"\">디지털</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54bde4db-c27a-4144-a85f-cf48c20cc2d2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-49399a7d-ee5f-43f7-9e16-fa504db6520a\" style=\"\">10~100개</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 33.33%; height: 43.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-989cfd0c-9a97-405c-9380-625464e3ea00\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-358c31a7-9483-497b-a734-a8685e2ad6ba\" style=\"\">종이, 사이즈 등</span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f8b38252-3e1d-4d65-81d3-11cbf4e0e8ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54138191-7793-4107-9c7f-476640f20b47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bea980c1-26eb-4a3d-a2d1-0cd4523b5d12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 언제 어디서든 문의를 환영합니다. 가장 합리적인 수량을 제안 드리겠습니다. 하지만 단상자가 아닌 싸바리박스나 골판지 합지는 소량 생산이 불가능할지 모릅니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4444c4f1-a3e1-478f-84c2-a0e040f0649e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f6597aaf-6594-4884-903a-af281d5d3fbc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c337ebb8-9c17-4b65-bfb1-0bab04eddef5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4892019-6213-4b7e-9dbe-d68ef90b8442\" style=\"color:#555555;\">마지막으로 고민해야 하는 것은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0ac0585a-7568-4dd0-b9c2-b2f079eeefbd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-326566bb-8797-45e0-9966-19302c139499\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2ca58eaa-c702-4f70-8aa8-beea96baa568\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9edadd17-0adc-49c1-9d1f-612f4749da5f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">거의 대부분 저희에게 문의하는 질문 중 많은 것은 납기입니다. 급한데 디지털로 빠르게 제작할 수 있는지에 대한 문의입니다. 오프셋은 기본적으로 5~7일 정도 소요되지만 디지털 인쇄 방식으로 2~3일 만에 가능한지의 질문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7df8a058-4ee6-4569-af85-01bf608e76ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e87aaea5-41ff-4444-b749-f0580ee9738d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11067f9d-edba-45b5-b024-42a933d21c50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7964b3b6-4769-45f1-ad19-3ada25d6aa55\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">결론만 말씀드리면 디지털로 2~3일 100개 생산은 가능합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-450cdd5e-82b1-4fb6-82e4-cc3182aff192\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8887649c-1a26-48df-a592-c18f2a120bd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cce66fcd-1efa-48dc-91a9-02739871319e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-47787528-ee1e-4457-bf28-aa4f5f7740b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자의 디지털 인쇄는 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 생산 시스템만으로 여러 번의 시행착오를 거쳐 100개를 2~3일 안에 납품할 수 있는 기초를 확립했습니다. 물론 종이, 사이즈, 후공정에 따라 불가능할 수 있지만 보통의 경우라면 대부분 납품하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83b5f4b3-21b7-4fe5-92c2-2b7131c2d148\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:687px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ea3485a8-c7d4-469b-b591-6ac7a9bf4020\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:632px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223923680638/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2c5bf831-1697-4059-b7b1-ecc9276baded\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfc37945-7dbf-4f26-88c0-5f36605b0ae2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff79a57d-2832-427f-974f-f4523f634f43\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 내용들은 거의 대부분 2~3일 안에 제작하여 납품했습니다. 저희도 생산시설 상황에 따른 변수가 많습니다. 하지만 고객과의 소통을 통해 많은 부분을 협력하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6bbeffab-2cf2-492a-9198-4eaa977c354f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-37ec913d-8b60-4a48-b335-b7031ee5723d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-f5bc77ff-6d8e-4b91-935e-acf328cf531f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fb116677-6986-43c1-a029-3c3697ecf231\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-498c479c-68d6-4aaf-8dca-5bf9d2d2436a\" style=\"\">결론</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4c3369d3-e4dc-4175-822c-35aed73e1f91\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0778b298-53bd-42c1-bbe4-0beed1aa9bfb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ce07e90d-a5d8-4aaf-a8c8-5bcdd092d9de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스타트 업 회사는 판매하는 제품의 성향에 따라 단상자를 제작해야 합니다. 위에서 말한 부분을 빼고도 여러 가지를 추가로 고려해야 하는 것들이 많습니다. 선대 포함 여부, 박 인쇄 등의 후공정 추가, 납품 방법 등등입니다. 이런 디테일한 모든 것을 상담해 드리겠습니다. 거래 유무를 떠나 반드시 문의하시고 제작하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49793e20-9858-4f09-8f72-ac4e8c0489dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c7c08e5-4f09-44f9-a49e-5024a51a5afa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e5fce18e-7b26-4cf7-8a29-8fe8be1a943d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5da9b0fa-21a3-4397-8d8b-f6f799dacd3b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 패키지 속에 담을 제품의 유형과 수량, 사이즈 등등을 상담을 통해 진행하고 있습니다. 수량이 많거나 거래처의 수준에 따라 방문 상담도 가능합니다. 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-99169b3c-1918-4d7a-9ec9-8b019522c831\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0531d9bb-07b1-4bfb-a43b-db0a4949b79b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223923680638#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}